data.description: Bring the critters! With over 16 acres you'll have plenty of room to roam! This charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is full of character and has been well cared for. The land is amazing - fenced in pasture, 2 metal sheds, large double door workshop, lean to shed, hunting cabin and all of this with a view of Lake Taneycomo. Enjoy your evenings out on the deck or sitting around the firepit. Rockaway Beach has several local restaurants, shopping and entertainment. ** Do not enter the fence with horses **
